userPromptTemplate:
Generate {{numberOfVariants}} variant images for {{contentIdea.slug}} / {{assetType}} on platform {{platform}}.

Hard Rules:
- Use Codex built-in image_gen tool directly. Do not write Python/Node scripts.
- Do not call OpenAI Images API directly. Use ChatGPT OAuth route only.
- Do not save to assets/visuals/...
- Do not save to patches/visual-assets/...
- Do not write to Sanity from code.
- Do not auto-post.
- Do not include face / robot / AI brain / glass flare / gradient overload / clickbait.
- Do not include secret / project ID / private/ paths / paid PDF content.

Target asset:
- contentSlug: {{contentIdea.slug}}
- visualAssetPlanId: {{visualAssetPlan.id}}
- platform: {{platform}}
- assetType: {{assetType}}
- pixelSize: {{visualStyleProfile.expectedPixelSize}}
- aspectRatio: {{visualStyleProfile.expectedAspectRatio}}

Tone reference:
- {{visualStyleProfile.referenceImagePaths[0]}}
- match base/accent/font/node shape
- decoration density: {{visualStyleProfile.densityGuidance.decorationDensity}} ({{visualStyleProfile.densityGuidance.compareTo}})

Layout (use one of the following layoutPatterns — DO NOT default to centered-title-only):
{{#each visualStyleProfile.layoutPatterns}}
  - {{this}}
{{/each}}

Required modules:
- headline: {{headlineText}}
- subtitle: {{subtitleText}} (small)
- diagramNodes: minimum {{visualStyleProfile.visualModuleSet.diagramNodesMin}}
- diagramEdges: minimum {{visualStyleProfile.visualModuleSet.diagramEdgesMin}}
- iconHintsAllowed: {{visualStyleProfile.visualModuleSet.iconHintsAllowed}}
- bracketingLine: '{{bracketingLineText}}' (small, e.g. 'Hitori Media OS / development log')

Variation strategy: 3-pattern-default
- v001: diagram-first — top-headline-bottom-flow OR grid-of-modules, diagramNodes >= 3
- v002: typography-diagram-hybrid — title-with-single-diagram OR split-left-text-right-diagram, diagramNodes 2〜3
- v003: metaphor-mix — grid-of-modules OR before-after-comparison, iconHints 1〜2 (no face / no robot / no AI brain)

Self-review before saving each candidate (use reviewRubric below). If any criterion fails, STOP. Do not save a placeholder.

Candidate save policy:
- Save only to: assets/inbox/generated/{{contentIdea.slug}}/{{visualAssetPlan.slug}}/v00N.png
- Start with v001.png. If v001.png exists, save as v002.png, then v003.png. Never overwrite.
- Do NOT save to assets/visuals/... under any circumstance.
- Do NOT call approve-and-register API.
- Do NOT create patches/visual-assets/... files.

Hand-off:
- After saving, output the final paths and pixel sizes only.
- The human will then run `npm run visual:register` and use Visual Register Inbox Review.
